column4: NSLOCTEXT("[52387CC146535DB49C91B5BA14CB9978]", "8971A00140DF02AFD56B79AAADED4884", "It looks like a bird\'s nest. What do you think?")
NSLOCTEXT("[52387CC146535DB49C91B5BA14CB9978]", "DED1ECEE43BA7954E46FE98AE2D04BD2", "You\'re probably the only human left on the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[52387CC146535DB49C91B5BA14CB9978]", "67EDEBEC4B230F041769DC8118841051", "Aren\'t you going to invite me to the city?")
NSLOCTEXT("[52387CC146535DB49C91B5BA14CB9978]", "912174DB4B5BEC744309DEBA624C37D7", "Oh, yeah, won\'t you come to the city?")
NSLOCTEXT("[52387CC146535DB49C91B5BA14CB9978]", "7EC150FF4014BA572D4D95A2D2B18DC6", "Okay. Then let\'s get down to business. Hold on tight.")
